org.apache.logging.log4j.core.appender.db.nosql.NoSQLObject

  • Packages that use NoSQLObject 
    Package Description
    org.apache.logging.log4j.core.appender.db.nosql
    The NoSQL Appender supports writing log events to NoSQL databases.
    org.apache.logging.log4j.core.appender.db.nosql.couchdb
    The classes in this package contain the Apache CouchDB provider for the NoSQL Appender.
    org.apache.logging.log4j.core.appender.db.nosql.mongodb
    The classes in this package contain the MongoDB provider for the NoSQL Appender.
